casebody.data:
Third Department,

December, 1966

(December 5, 1966) Mabelle H. Whitfield, Respondent, v. Robert D. Whitfield, Appellant.

'Appeal dismissed, without costs, unless appellant shall, on or before December 28, 1966, file and serve record, brief and notice of argument for the term commencing February 6, 1967, in which event motion denied. Motion for a stay denied (see CPLR 5519, subd. [a], par. 2). Gibson, P. J., Herlihy, Reynolds, Staley, Jr., and Brink, JJ., concur.
